5:
Ehehe, I can't believe I'm at the
beach with my Nimby-Wimby!
Ehehehe!
9:
Yeah, I can't believe it either... But I
promised, so here we are...
15: Look, look! Do you see all this sand?
34:
I think your standards for "fun" are
pretty low here!
38:
As long as I'm with you, I'm always
having fun! Besides, this TOTALLY
beats practice!
41:
Sure... Long as you're having fun, I
guess I can't complain.
44:
Waaah! Mama! Papa! Where are
you?!
47:
Well, would you look at that. A
beastfolk kid. Ugh, I'm so jealousss
that someone got to pop one out
before me!
51:
Cut that out, you're gonna scare the
crap outta him. Let me handle this.
54:
Hey, kid. What do your parents look
like? Did they tell you to meet them
anywhere?
57:
*sniffle* My papa's beastfolk... and
my mama's an apothecary...
69:
The hell he is! The possibility of that
is beyond zero, ya hear me?!
74:
Gosh, can you imagine us having a
little pip-squeak of our own? Ehehe...
Hehehehe!
93:
Eeeek! Y-you're the white monster
from before! I thought Alk and
Shywe helped me get rid of you!
97:
S-somebody heeeelp meee! Get
this thing away from meee!
103:
Maybe if I get lucky... the ground will
open up and swallow me whole...
108:
Thank you for looking after my kid! I
seriously owe you one!
110:
Er, don't worry about it. Seriously. I'd
like to forget any of that ever
happened...
114:
I-I'm so sorry... It's partially my fault
for panicking like that.
118:
It's fine. I'm more than used to you
causing a scene.
126:
Then I apologize for all those other
times... though I'm sure this apology
comes a little too late...
130: Ugh, this is making my head spin...
134: Listen, can I call you Sohvi?
138:
Oh, that's fine! But... I don't know if
giving me a name matters...
140:
I'll probably be gone soon, like a
dream that vanishes as soon as you
open your eyes.
158:
A-ah, it's just... I'm so happy right
now.
161:
You see, it's always been a dream of
mine to spend time at the beach
with a boyfriend...
164:
Just enjoying the sand and the
waves together...
169:
B-but... Ah, I'm so sorry! I just...
thought of you as my boyfriend,
without even asking... I'm so gross...
177:
Th-thank you... for being so nice
about it...
186: Huh? Nimbus... Did I fall asleep?
191:
Is that the sun setting on the
horizon?! Did I just WASTE my entire
day out with you?!
195:
Wait, are there tears... in my eyes?
Did sand get in there or something?
197:
Why is there a sense of satisfaction
in my chest... even though I was out
for half the day?
200:
...All I can say is, today wasn't half
bad.
209: Well, if you're happy, then whatever!
